name: Earth Observation day
description: Join us in recognizing the value of seeing Earth from a new perspective! Earth Observation Day is a celebration of the many ways we study our planet from above. Through satellites, aerial imagery, and other technologies, Earth observation helps us better understand weather, climate, natural resources, and the changing environment. This day highlights the importance of monitoring our world to support science, sustainability, and everyday decision-making.
